  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Cooky\u2605Yummy Way",
      "effect": "1 Tuner + 1 non-Tuner monster\nFor this card's Synchro Summon, you can treat 1 Link-1 monster you control as a Level 1 Tuner. You can only use each of the following effects of \"Cooky\u2606Yummy Way\" once per turn. If this card is Synchro Summoned: You can target up to 2 face-up monsters on the field; change them to face-down Defense Position. When your opponent activates a card or effect (Quick Effect): You can return this card to the Extra Deck; Special Summon up to 2 \"Yummy\" monsters from your GY.",
      "official": false
    },
